Package: rmdTemplates
Type: Package
Title: A collection of Rmarkdown templates
Version: 0.9.2
Author: F. Rodriguez-Sanchez <f.rodriguez.sanc@gmail.com>. 
Maintainer: F. Rodriguez-Sanchez <f.rodriguez.sanc@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of Rmarkdown templates for writing scientific manuscripts, 
    manuscript reviews, Beamer slides (metropolis theme) 
    and other Rmarkdown documents, with support for cross-references, 
    citations and different bibliography styles. 
License: CC0
URL: https://github.com/Pakillo/rmdTemplates
